{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "ewcxxtylng8",
    "category": "news",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EWCxxtYLng8",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is very dark tonight.",
      "zh": "今晚很黑暗。",
      "ja": "今夜はとても暗いです。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go inside.",
      "zh": "我們進去吧。",
      "ja": "中に入りましょう。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, look at the front door.",
      "zh": "爸爸，看看前門。",
      "ja": "お父さん、玄関のドアを見て。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is wide open.",
      "zh": "門大開著。",
      "ja": "大きく開いています。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is not closed.",
      "zh": "沒有關上。",
      "ja": "閉まっていません。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop everyone.",
      "zh": "大家停下。",
      "ja": "みんな止まって。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Red alert.",
      "zh": "紅色警報。",
      "ja": "赤色警報。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Danger.",
      "zh": "危險。",
      "ja": "危険です。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ethan, what is wrong?",
      "zh": "伊森，怎麼了？",
      "ja": "イーサン、どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The door is open.",
      "zh": "門是開著的。",
      "ja": "ドアが開いています。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I closed it today.",
      "zh": "但我今天有關上。",
      "ja": "でも今日閉めたはずです。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think.",
      "zh": "我想是這樣。",
      "ja": "たぶん。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no!",
      "zh": "喔不！",
      "ja": "ああ、いや！",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did a bad monster open the door?",
      "zh": "是壞怪物開了門嗎？",
      "ja": "悪いモンスターがドアを開けたの？",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, Leo.",
      "zh": "不是，Leo。",
      "ja": "違うよ、レオ。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not a monster.",
      "zh": "不是怪物。",
      "ja": "モンスターじゃない。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A thief.",
      "zh": "是小偷。",
      "ja": "泥棒だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Someone took our things.",
      "zh": "有人拿走了我們的東西。",
      "ja": "誰かが私たちの物を持っていった。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A thief?",
      "zh": "小偷？",
      "ja": "泥棒？",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is very bad.",
      "zh": "那很糟糕。",
      "ja": "それはとても悪いことだ。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, we must be careful.",
      "zh": "是的，我們必須小心。",
      "ja": "はい、気をつけなければ。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He can be inside.",
      "zh": "他可能還在裡面。",
      "ja": "彼は中にいるかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Inside?",
      "zh": "裡面？",
      "ja": "中に？",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right now, I am scared, Mommy.",
      "zh": "媽媽，我現在很害怕。",
      "ja": "今、怖いよ、お母さん。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay close to me, Maya.",
      "zh": "瑪雅，靠近我。",
      "ja": "マヤ、私のそばにいて。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hold my hand.",
      "zh": "握著我的手。",
      "ja": "手を握って。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not worry.",
      "zh": "別擔心。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will go inside first.",
      "zh": "我先進去。",
      "ja": "私が先に入るよ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay here in the yard.",
      "zh": "你們留在院子裡。",
      "ja": "ここで庭にいて。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will check the rooms.",
      "zh": "我會檢查房間。",
      "ja": "部屋を調べるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "有人嗎？",
      "ja": "こんにちは？",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is anybody here?",
      "zh": "有人在嗎？",
      "ja": "誰かいますか？",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Show yourself.",
      "zh": "出來吧。",
      "ja": "姿を見せて。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am coming in.",
      "zh": "我要進去了。",
      "ja": "入るよ。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please be careful, Ethan.",
      "zh": "伊森，小心點。",
      "ja": "気をつけて、イーサン。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is safe.",
      "zh": "安全的。",
      "ja": "安全だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The room is empty.",
      "zh": "房間是空的。",
      "ja": "部屋は空っぽだ。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will turn on the light.",
      "zh": "我會開燈。",
      "ja": "電気をつけるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is the thief gone, Dad?",
      "zh": "小偷走了嗎，爸爸？",
      "ja": "泥棒はもういないの？お父さん。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nobody is here.",
      "zh": "沒有人在這裡。",
      "ja": "誰もいません。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can come in now.",
      "zh": "你們現在可以進來了。",
      "ja": "今入っていいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh my goodness.",
      "zh": "天啊。",
      "ja": "まあ！",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What a big mess.",
      "zh": "好亂啊。",
      "ja": "すごく散らかっている。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My toys.",
      "zh": "我的玩具。",
      "ja": "私のおもちゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My dolls and blocks are on the floor.",
      "zh": "我的娃娃和積木都掉在地上。",
      "ja": "私の人形とブロックが床に散らばっている。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And look at the bookshelf.",
      "zh": "還有看看書架。",
      "ja": "それに本棚を見て。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All the books are on the carpet.",
      "zh": "所有書都掉在地毯上。",
      "ja": "本が全部カーペットの上にある。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The living room is destroyed.",
      "zh": "客廳被弄壞了。",
      "ja": "リビングルームがめちゃくちゃだ。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is very dirty.",
      "zh": "非常髒亂。",
      "ja": "とても汚れている。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He opened all the drawers.",
      "zh": "他把所有抽屜都打開了。",
      "ja": "彼はすべての引き出しを開けた。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He was looking for money.",
      "zh": "他在找錢。",
      "ja": "お金を探していた。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, look at the table.",
      "zh": "爸爸，看桌子。",
      "ja": "お父さん、テーブルを見て。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The TV is gone.",
      "zh": "電視不見了。",
      "ja": "テレビがなくなっている。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, Leo.",
      "zh": "是的，Leo。",
      "ja": "そうだよ、レオ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our house was robbed.",
      "zh": "我們家被搶劫了。",
      "ja": "私たちの家が強盗にあった。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The thief took our big television.",
      "zh": "小偷拿走了我們的大電視。",
      "ja": "泥棒は大きなテレビを持っていった。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's check the kitchen.",
      "zh": "我們去廚房看看。",
      "ja": "キッチンを調べよう。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The room where we cook.",
      "zh": "我們做飯的房間。",
      "ja": "料理をする部屋。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look, Mom.",
      "zh": "媽媽，看。",
      "ja": "お母さん、見て。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The refrigerator is open.",
      "zh": "冰箱開著。",
      "ja": "冷蔵庫が開いている。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And there is milk and juice on the floor.",
      "zh": "牛奶和果汁倒在地上。",
      "ja": "ミルクとジュースが床にこぼれている。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My yellow plates are broken on the floor.",
      "zh": "我的黃色盤子摔破了。",
      "ja": "私の黄色い皿が床で割れている。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He made a big mess in the kitchen too.",
      "zh": "他也把廚房弄得很亂。",
      "ja": "彼はキッチンもめちゃくちゃにした。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And he even ate our chocolate cookies.",
      "zh": "他甚至吃了我們的巧克力餅乾。",
      "ja": "そしてチョコレートクッキーまで食べた。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is very mean.",
      "zh": "那很壞。",
      "ja": "それはとても意地悪だ。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love those cookies.",
      "zh": "我很喜歡那些餅乾。",
      "ja": "あのクッキーが大好き。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He was very hungry and very bad.",
      "zh": "他又餓又壞。",
      "ja": "彼はとてもお腹が空いていて悪かった。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on team.",
      "zh": "來吧，團隊。",
      "ja": "さあ、チーム。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's check upstairs.",
      "zh": "我們去樓上看看。",
      "ja": "上の階を調べよう。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's check the bedroom.",
      "zh": "我們去臥室看看。",
      "ja": "寝室を調べよう。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All my clothes are on the bed.",
      "zh": "我所有的衣服都在床上。",
      "ja": "私の服が全部ベッドの上にある。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And my clothes are on the floor.",
      "zh": "我的衣服也在地上。",
      "ja": "服も床に散らばっている。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My jewelry box is open.",
      "zh": "我的珠寶盒打開了。",
      "ja": "私の宝石箱が開いている。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did he take everything, Mommy?",
      "zh": "他把所有東西都拿走了嗎，媽媽？",
      "ja": "全部持っていったの？お母さん。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My rings and necklaces are missing.",
      "zh": "我的戒指和項鍊不見了。",
      "ja": "私の指輪とネックレスがなくなっている。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mommy is crying.",
      "zh": "媽媽在哭。",
      "ja": "お母さんが泣いている。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She is very sad.",
      "zh": "她很難過。",
      "ja": "とても悲しんでいる。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not cry, Grace.",
      "zh": "不要哭，Grace。",
      "ja": "泣かないで、グレース。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please do not be sad.",
      "zh": "請不要難過。",
      "ja": "悲しまないで。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at us.",
      "zh": "看看我們。",
      "ja": "私たちを見て。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are safe.",
      "zh": "我們很安全。",
      "ja": "私たちは安全だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nobody is hurt.",
      "zh": "沒有人受傷。",
      "ja": "誰も怪我していない。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But Dad, the television and the rings are gone.",
      "zh": "但是爸爸，電視和戒指都不見了。",
      "ja": "でもお父さん、テレビと指輪がなくなった。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is okay, Leo.",
      "zh": "沒關係，Leo。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ、レオ。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can buy new things.",
      "zh": "我們可以買新的東西。",
      "ja": "新しいものを買えるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our family is safe.",
      "zh": "我們的家人很安全。",
      "ja": "家族は安全だ。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is the most precious thing.",
      "zh": "那是最珍貴的事。",
      "ja": "それが一番大切なことだ。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are right, Ethan.",
      "zh": "你說得對，伊森。",
      "ja": "その通りだよ、イーサン。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My family is here.",
      "zh": "我的家人在這裡。",
      "ja": "家族がここにいる。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now, I will call the police to help us.",
      "zh": "現在，我會打電話給警察幫忙。",
      "ja": "今、警察に助けを呼ぶよ。",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello 911.",
      "zh": "你好，911。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、911です。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our house was robbed.",
      "zh": "我們家被搶劫了。",
      "ja": "私たちの家が強盗にあった。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please send help.",
      "zh": "請派人來幫忙。",
      "ja": "助けを送ってください。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look outside.",
      "zh": "看看外面。",
      "ja": "外を見て。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Flashing blue and red lights.",
      "zh": "閃爍的藍紅燈光。",
      "ja": "青と赤の点滅ライト。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good evening family.",
      "zh": "晚上好，家人們。",
      "ja": "こんばんは、家族の皆さん。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am Officer Bob.",
      "zh": "我是警官Bob。",
      "ja": "私はボブ警官です。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am a policeman.",
      "zh": "我是一名警察。",
      "ja": "私は警察官です。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I catch bad guys.",
      "zh": "我抓壞人。",
      "ja": "悪者を捕まえます。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello Officer.",
      "zh": "你好，警官。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、警官さん。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A thief stole our TV.",
      "zh": "小偷偷了我們的電視。",
      "ja": "泥棒がテレビを盗みました。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am sorry to hear that.",
      "zh": "聽到這個我很難過。",
      "ja": "それはお気の毒に。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me check the front door.",
      "zh": "讓我檢查前門。",
      "ja": "玄関のドアを調べます。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did the thief break the door, Officer?",
      "zh": "警官，小偷有破壞門嗎？",
      "ja": "泥棒はドアを壊しましたか、警官？",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The window is not broken.",
      "zh": "窗戶沒有破。",
      "ja": "窓は壊れていません。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The door is fine.",
      "zh": "門沒事。",
      "ja": "ドアは大丈夫です。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you lock the door with a key?",
      "zh": "你有用鑰匙鎖門嗎？",
      "ja": "鍵でドアをロックしましたか？",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I remember now.",
      "zh": "我現在想起來了。",
      "ja": "今思い出した。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was in a big hurry today.",
      "zh": "我今天很匆忙。",
      "ja": "今日はとても急いでいた。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was not thinking.",
      "zh": "我沒多想。",
      "ja": "考えていなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ethan, you forgot to lock the front door?",
      "zh": "伊森，你忘了鎖前門？",
      "ja": "イーサン、玄関のドアをロックし忘れたの？",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am so sorry Grace.",
      "zh": "對不起，Grace。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、グレース。",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was my mistake.",
      "zh": "是我的錯。",
      "ja": "私のミスです。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel so bad about my mistake.",
      "zh": "我對我的錯誤感到很難過。",
      "ja": "自分のミスがとても悪いと感じている。",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is my fault.",
      "zh": "是我的錯。",
      "ja": "私のせいです。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I put our family in danger.",
      "zh": "我讓我們家人陷入危險。",
      "ja": "家族を危険にさらした。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please forgive me.",
      "zh": "請原諒我。",
      "ja": "許してください。",
      "time": "00:04:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is okay, Ethan.",
      "zh": "沒關係，伊森。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ、イーサン。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We all make mistakes.",
      "zh": "我們都會犯錯。",
      "ja": "誰でも間違いをする。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not be sad, Dad.",
      "zh": "不要難過，爸爸。",
      "ja": "悲しまないで、お父さん。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We love you.",
      "zh": "我們愛你。",
      "ja": "私たちはあなたを愛している。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your family is right Dad.",
      "zh": "你的家人說得對，爸爸。",
      "ja": "家族の言う通りだよ、お父さん。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not be sad.",
      "zh": "不要難過。",
      "ja": "悲しまないで。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I will give you some safety tips for next time.",
      "zh": "但我會給你一些安全建議，下次注意。",
      "ja": "でも次のために安全のヒントを教えるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "First, always check the locks two times before you leave.",
      "zh": "第一，離開前一定要檢查兩次鎖。",
      "ja": "まず、出かける前に鍵を二度確認すること。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Check the doors and check the windows.",
      "zh": "檢查門和窗戶。",
      "ja": "ドアと窓をチェックする。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Second, you must have good communication with your neighbors.",
      "zh": "第二，你必須和鄰居保持良好溝通。",
      "ja": "次に、隣人と良いコミュニケーションを持つこと。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You must talk to them when something bad happens.",
      "zh": "發生壞事時要和他們說。",
      "ja": "悪いことが起きたら話すこと。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We will talk to them tomorrow morning.",
      "zh": "我們明天早上會和他們談談。",
      "ja": "明日の朝、話すよ。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now let's find clues to solve the mystery.",
      "zh": "現在讓我們找線索解開謎團。",
      "ja": "さあ、手がかりを見つけて謎を解こう。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at the floor, Officer Bob.",
      "zh": "看地板，Bob警官。",
      "ja": "床を見て、ボブ警官。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me use my bright flashlight.",
      "zh": "讓我用明亮的手電筒。",
      "ja": "明るい懐中電灯を使わせて。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is it, Officer?",
      "zh": "那是什麼，警官？",
      "ja": "何ですか、警官？",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do you see?",
      "zh": "你看到了什麼？",
      "ja": "何が見えますか？",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Muddy footprints from dirty shoes.",
      "zh": "髒鞋留下的泥腳印。",
      "ja": "汚れた靴の泥の足跡。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He made our clean carpet very dirty.",
      "zh": "他把我們乾淨的地毯弄得很髒。",
      "ja": "彼はきれいなカーペットをとても汚した。",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Follow me.",
      "zh": "跟我來。",
      "ja": "ついてきて。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The footprints go out the back door.",
      "zh": "腳印通往後門。",
      "ja": "足跡は裏口へ続いている。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go to the backyard.",
      "zh": "我們去後院。",
      "ja": "裏庭に行こう。",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hurry.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "急いで。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is very dark in the backyard.",
      "zh": "後院很黑。",
      "ja": "裏庭はとても暗い。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay close to us kids.",
      "zh": "孩子們靠近我們。",
      "ja": "子供たち、私たちに近づいて。",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My flashlight shows the footprints.",
      "zh": "我的手電筒照出腳印。",
      "ja": "懐中電灯が足跡を照らしている。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They go to the tall wooden fence.",
      "zh": "腳印通往高木柵欄。",
      "ja": "足跡は高い木のフェンスへ続いている。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at the grass.",
      "zh": "看看草地。",
      "ja": "草を見て。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There is no TV here.",
      "zh": "這裡沒有電視。",
      "ja": "ここにテレビはない。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A no jewelry box.",
      "zh": "也沒有珠寶盒。",
      "ja": "宝石箱もない。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did the thief take out things?",
      "zh": "小偷拿出東西了嗎？",
      "ja": "泥棒は物を持ち出した？",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The thief took them.",
      "zh": "小偷拿走了。",
      "ja": "泥棒が持っていった。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He ran away.",
      "zh": "他逃跑了。",
      "ja": "彼は逃げた。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Listen family, we have many similar robberies here.",
      "zh": "聽著家人們，這裡有很多類似的搶劫案。",
      "ja": "聞いて、家族のみんな、ここでは似たような強盗が多い。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Many houses near here were robbed this week.",
      "zh": "這週附近很多房子被搶劫。",
      "ja": "今週、この近くの多くの家が強盗にあった。",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So we cannot be careless.",
      "zh": "所以我們不能大意。",
      "ja": "だから油断できない。",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We must be alert.",
      "zh": "我們必須保持警覺。",
      "ja": "警戒しなければ。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you catch him, Officer Bob?",
      "zh": "你能抓到他嗎，Bob警官？",
      "ja": "彼を捕まえられますか、ボブ警官？",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We have a suspect.",
      "zh": "我們有嫌疑犯。",
      "ja": "容疑者がいる。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We know who he is.",
      "zh": "我們知道他是誰。",
      "ja": "彼が誰か知っている。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where is he?",
      "zh": "他在哪裡？",
      "ja": "彼はどこ？",
      "time": "00:06:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He is very fast.",
      "zh": "他很快。",
      "ja": "彼はとても速い。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I will investigate and find him.",
      "zh": "但我會調查並找到他。",
      "ja": "でも調査して見つけるよ。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good morning, Mr. Clark.",
      "zh": "早安，Clark先生。",
      "ja": "おはようございます、クラークさん。",
      "time": "00:06:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good morning, Grace.",
      "zh": "早安，Grace。",
      "ja": "おはよう、グレース。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is everything okay?",
      "zh": "一切都好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫ですか？",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our house was robbed last night.",
      "zh": "我們家昨晚被搶劫了。",
      "ja": "昨夜、私たちの家が強盗にあった。",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is terrible.",
      "zh": "那真糟糕。",
      "ja": "それはひどい。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The thief took our TV and some rings.",
      "zh": "小偷拿走了我們的電視和一些戒指。",
      "ja": "泥棒はテレビと指輪を持っていった。",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have security cameras on my house.",
      "zh": "我家有監視攝影機。",
      "ja": "私の家には防犯カメラがある。",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will check the videos for you.",
      "zh": "我會幫你們查看錄影。",
      "ja": "ビデオをチェックしてあげる。",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mr. Clark.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，Clark先生。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、クラークさん。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We must look out for each other.",
      "zh": "我們必須互相照顧。",
      "ja": "お互いに気をつけなければ。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good neighbors help each other.",
      "zh": "好鄰居會互相幫助。",
      "ja": "良い隣人は助け合う。",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is a new beautiful day.",
      "zh": "這是新的一天，美好的一天。",
      "ja": "新しい美しい日だ。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's clean our house, family.",
      "zh": "家人們，我們來打掃家裡。",
      "ja": "家族のみんな、家を掃除しよう。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The living room is very dirty.",
      "zh": "客廳很髒。",
      "ja": "リビングルームがとても汚れている。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will pick up my toys.",
      "zh": "我要撿起我的玩具。",
      "ja": "おもちゃを片付けるよ。",
      "time": "00:07:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will clean the dirty carpet.",
      "zh": "我要清理髒地毯。",
      "ja": "汚れたカーペットを掃除する。",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will put the books on the bookshelf.",
      "zh": "我要把書放回書架。",
      "ja": "本を本棚に戻す。",
      "time": "00:07:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The cookie jar is empty on the table.",
      "zh": "桌上的餅乾罐是空的。",
      "ja": "テーブルのクッキージャーは空っぽだ。",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can bake new cookies today.",
      "zh": "我們今天可以烤新的餅乾。",
      "ja": "今日新しいクッキーを焼こう。",
      "time": "00:07:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yay.",
      "zh": "耶。",
      "ja": "やった。",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love sweet chocolate cookies.",
      "zh": "我喜歡甜甜的巧克力餅乾。",
      "ja": "甘いチョコレートクッキーが大好き。",
      "time": "00:07:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I will sweep the kitchen floor.",
      "zh": "我會掃廚房地板。",
      "ja": "キッチンの床を掃くよ。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, team.",
      "zh": "謝謝你們，團隊。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、チーム。",
      "time": "00:07:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are great helpers.",
      "zh": "你們是很棒的幫手。",
      "ja": "君たちは素晴らしい助っ人だ。",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Our house is clean and beautiful again.",
      "zh": "我們的家又乾淨又漂亮了。",
      "ja": "家がまたきれいで美しくなった。",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look.",
